        "rich_text_cPbJNJ": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Setting A Budget Without Compromise  ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Setting A Budget Without Compromise  </h2><p>While there is said to be a thumb rule to invest three months’ salary to buy an engagement ring, there is no such rule! Love has no price tag. Setting a smart budget means getting a luxurious ring that aligns with your lifestyle and values. Natural diamonds cost a lot more than lab grown diamonds, while lab grown diamonds are scientifically and optically the same as natural diamonds. Lab grown diamonds are 100% real diamonds, that come with more customization options while giving more diamond clarity. They are ethically sourced, making the same the better option that provides more value and sparkle while being eco-friendly. While choosing an engagement ring, choose a ring style that is a balance of both timeless and trending. </p>",
            "custom_id": "setting",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_QHPMTH": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Must-Know Checklist to Choosing the Perfect Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Must-Know Checklist to Choosing the Perfect Engagement Ring</h2><p>Before saying “yes” to the ring, double-check these essentials:</p><p>1.Choose a diamond with a balanced 4C profile<br/>2.Ensure the metal complements your partner’s skin tone and lifestyle<br/>3.Get the right ring size discreetly or through a close friend<br/>4.Review warranty, maintenance, and resizing policies<br/>5.Take your time - the perfect ring feels right when you see it<br/>6.Most importantly, always ask for jewelry certification and the details of every diamond </p>",
            "custom_id": "the-must",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3fBN74": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>Selecting the perfect engagement ring becomes effortless when guided by trusted jewelry experts. More than just an accessory, an engagement ring is a timeless symbol of love, commitment, and the beautiful journey you’ll share together. At <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lucira Jewelry\">Lucira Jewelry</a>, we take pride in crafting each piece with precision, offering ethically sourced diamonds, exceptional designs, and swift delivery, ensuring that every love story we touch is filled with love, comfort and joy. </p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        }
